  "link": "http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p728316/", 
  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Spotlight\" target=\"_blank\">Spotlight</a><br />\n\tA spotlight is a bright light with a specific focus. Where is the spotlight? Why is it used? How do people react to it?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They turned on the spotlight... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) spotlight on an actor doing a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/soliloquy\" target=\"_blank\">soliloquy</a> of a play on stage<br />\n\t2) spotlight on the award winner as the person when on stage to accept the award<br />\n\t3) a company was in the spotlight recently for malpractice<br />\n\t4) new articles spotlighted social issues<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThis is <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/overkill\" target=\"_blank\">overkill</a>, he thought as he stepped into the venue, and the spotlight was immediately put on him. He is used to being the center of attention, being in the public eye and being in front of flashing camera lights, but this spotlight putting him on the spot, literally, seemed to him unnecessary. With or without spotlights, his entrance anywhere would turn heads. Displaying his signature smile as always, he nodded and waved to guests greeting him, before he was <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/whisk\" target=\"_blank\">whisk</a>ed away by the staff leading him toward the VIP section to meet the corporate clients.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162830182031/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p728316/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p728316\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731141/\">2.25英寸法告诉你 该剪短发还是留长</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731252/\">专家预言：8种职业未来将被机器人代替！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731746/\">纯属搞笑：警惕&慎取 最容易出轨的英文名</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731748/\">对纸币说不 丹麦有望成为首个无现金国家</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731452/\">科学拯救吃货：你为什么总是饿？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731296/\">湿身狗狗哭丧脸：各种“原形毕露”笑翻天</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p731498/\">错不在我：学生二度挂科之后起诉学校</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161330/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 3 Sorry sir.</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p730988/\">遵循这个公式 人人都能成为复联超级英雄！</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
